            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>莫德納(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MRNA:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MRNA\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MRNA-US</a>)截至台北時間28日03:50股價下跌2.41美元，報45.58美元，跌幅5.02%，成交量11,101,822（股），盤中最高價51.18美元、最低價45.57美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：-0.86%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+0.5%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+1.01%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+2.52%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>莫德納(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MRNA:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MRNA\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MRNA-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：+13.28%</li> <li>近 1 月：+56.12%</li> <li>近 3 月：+82.71%</li> <li>近 6 月：+42.64%</li> <li>今年以來：+57.84%</li></ul></section></main>",
